## StaticDeconstructor type

This is a Deconstructor which you can call or use as-is

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
type StaticDeconstructor<T, F extends () => Deconstructor<T> = () => Deconstructor<T>> = F & Deconstructor<T>;
```
